::Aerotaur::
    He steps in front of Trinity deeply moved by her sorrow.  In an attempt 
to comfort her he again attempts robot mode.  He pulls his wings in around 
him and throws them back retaining them in his robot mode.  He looks at 
Trinity and quietly tells her "You have me and I will keep you safe and raise 
you."
